lead_paragraph: Scott Hend moved a shot clear of Sweden's Alex Noren after carding a five-under-par 65 in the third round of the European Masters at Crans-sur-Sierre Golf Club in Switzerland on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Golf: Australian Hend Takes One-Shot Lead at Crans-Sur-Sierre
